<p>You mentioned the one thing he got out of &#8220;7 Habbits&#8221;, the concern/influence distinctions.</p>
<p>I got a different one thing from that book about 20 years ago &#8212; the distinction between urgent and important.  There are many urgent things that can and should be ignored.  Then they go away.  It helped with time management.</p>
<p>Thanks for another great show.</p>
